headline: Growth Catalyst Group Adds More Industry Veterans to Power Next Phase of Growth
summary: Growth Catalyst Group of Companies (GCG), a global expert in tech-led supply chain solutions, today announced a major expansion of its leadership team. The company has appointed one new Senior Vice President and four new Vice Presidents to guide its next chapter of strategic, rapid growth.
